Enhanced with: - Hover effects (transform: translateY(-4px)) - Box shadows on hover - Icon + Title + Description + Tags + Link - Consistent spacing and styling - Technology badges with color coding



BEFORE: 8em (~128px), rounded corners AFTER: 280px, circle with white border, larger shadow Impact: More professional, commanding presence

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;  // Scales down from 3rem
    }
    .hero-stats {
        flex-direction: column;  // Stack vertically
        gap: 1rem;
    }
}
BEFORE: Long scrolling, difficult to navigate AFTER: Optimized card layout, proper text sizing, touch-friendly buttons
